 <H1>PROPPATCH Method - Motivation (Cont�d)</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Separation of Functionality
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Looking at real world implementations it seems likely that properties will be maintained on a server using one mechanism while a number of different mechanisms may be used to handle methods on non-property resources. So it would be useful to separate commands to alter properties from commands to alter resources.
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Solution
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Introduce the PROPPATCH method.</UL></UL></P>
<P></P> 
